Had such a great time hanging with my big bro @joshwex last week. 

This pic is from the day after his 1st brain surgery (of the 2) he’s had this past month, and thankfully, his recovery is going really well. 

Josh is a true inspiration. He’s been beating the odds for glioblastoma for 3 years, taking every challenge it throws at him head on. His positive attitude remains unmatched and his endless reservoir of patience never ceases to amaze anyone in his presence ♥️💫💫.

Please wish him a speedy recovery 🙏🏽.
